{% extends "base.html.twig" %}
{% block title %}Accueil - {% endblock %}
{% block description %}Laklé est une agence immobilière à vocation sociale (AIVS). Elle a la particularité
    de mobiliser des logements à loyer modéré dans le parc public et dans le parc privé pour mettre
    à disposition des personnes à faibles ressources, en apportant un maximum de garanties au propriétaire.{% endblock %}
{% block content %}
<aside id="fh5co-hero" class="js-fullheight">
    <div class="flexslider js-fullheight">
        <ul class="slides">
            <li style="background-image: url({{ asset('images/photo_home.jpeg') }});">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="col-md-12 text-center js-fullheight fh5co-property-brief slider-text">
                        <div class="fh5co-property-brief-inner">
                            <div class="fh5co-box">

                                <h3><a href="#">Propriétaires</a></h3>
                                <p style = "margin-top: 40px;">Vous cherchez à louer votre logement?</p>
                                <p>Vous exigez le maximum de garanties?</p>
                                <p>Vous souhaitez une mis en location immédiate?</p>
                                <p><a href="{{ path('proprietaires') }}" class="btn btn-primary">Laklé s'occupe de
                                        vous</a></p>


                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </li>

        </ul>
    </div>
</aside>
<div id="fh5co-presentation">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2 text-center fh5co-heading animate-box"
                 data-animate-effect="fadeIn">
                <h2>Qui sommes-nous?</h2>
                <p>Laklé est une agence immobilière à vocation sociale. Elle a la particularité de mobiliser des
                    logements
                    à loyers maîtrisés dans le parc public et dans le parc privé pour les mettre à disposition des
                    personnes
                    à faibles ressources, <strong>en apportant un maximum de garanties aux propriétaires</strong>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 item-block animate-box" data-animate-effect="fadeIn">


            </div>


        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div id="best-deal">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2 text-center fh5co-heading animate-box"
                 data-animate-effect="fadeIn">
                <h2>Derniers logements mis en ligne</h2>
            </div>
            {% for advert in lastAdverts %}
                <div class="col-md-4 item-block animate-box" data-animate-effect="fadeIn">


                    <div class="fh5co-property">
                        <figure>
                            <img src="{{ asset('uploads/adverts/images/' ~ advert.firstImage) }}"
                                 style="height:250px" class="img-responsive">
                            <a href="{{ path ('advert', {'id': advert.id}) }}" class="tag">Voir plus</a>
                        </figure>
                        <div class="fh5co-property-innter">
                            <h3><a href="#">{{ advert.address }}</a></h3>
                            <div class="price-status">
                                <span class="price">{{ advert.type }} </span>
                            </div>
                            <p>{{ advert.limitedText|raw }}</p>
                        </div>

                        <p class="fh5co-property-specification">
                            Loyer hors charges <span><strong>{{ advert.price }}€/mois</strong></span> <br>

                        </p>
                    </div>


                </div>
            {% endfor %}


        </div>
    </div>
</div>


<div id="fh5co-testimonial">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 text-center fh5co-heading animate-box"
                 data-animate-effect="fadeIn">
                <h2>Témoignages</h2>

            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 text-center item-block animate-box" data-animate-effect="fadeIn">
                <blockquote>
                    <p>&ldquo; She packed her seven versalia, put her initial into the belt and made herself on the
                        way. When she reached the first hills of the Italic Mountains, she had a last view back on
                        the skyline of her hometown Bookmarksgrove, the headline of. &rdquo;</p>
                    <p><span class="fh5co-author"><cite>Jason Davidson</cite></span></p>

                </blockquote>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 text-center item-block animate-box" data-animate-effect="fadeIn">
                <blockquote>
                    <p>&ldquo; Alphabet Village and the subline of her own road, the Line Lane. Pityful a rethoric
                        question ran over her cheek, then she continued her way. She had a last view back on the
                        skyline of her hometown Bookmarksgrove, the headline of. &rdquo;</p>
                    <p><span class="fh5co-author"><cite>Kyle Smith</cite></span></p>
                </blockquote>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 text-center item-block animate-box" data-animate-effect="fadeIn">

                <blockquote>
                    <p>&ldquo; The Big Oxmox advised her not to do so, because there were thousands of bad Commas,
                        wild Question Marks and devious Semikoli, but the Little Blind Text didn’t listen. S he had
